@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div class="container-fluid" style="width:100%; ">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">

            <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-indicators">
                    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-inner " style="width:100%; ">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img src="/images/slider 1.jpg" class="d-block w-100 " style="height: 600px; width:140%;">
                        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                            <h5>FIRST SLIDER</h5>
                            <p>Some representative placeholder content for the first slide.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="/Images/slider 2.jpg" class="d-block " style="height:600px; width:100%;">
                        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                            <h5>SECOND SLIDER</h5>
                            <p>Some representative placeholder content for the first slide.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="/Images/slider 3.jpg" class="d-block w-100 " style="height: 600px; width:140%;">
                        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                            <h5>THIRD SLIDER</h5>
                            <p>Some representative placeholder content for the first slide.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                </button>
                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="container-fluid mt-3">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4 mt-3">
                        <div class="card">
                            <img src="/images/babar_cover.jpg" alt="">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="card-title  text-center">Sports</div>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Sports encompass a wide range of physical activities and competitions that require skill, strategy, and physical prowess. They serve as a platform for individuals and teams to showcase their talents and push their limits. Whether in stadiums, on fields, or in arenas, sports have the power to inspire, entertain, and unite people across the globe.
                                </p>
                                <a href="" class="btn btn-success d-grid col-md-6 offset-3">Read More...</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mt-3">
                        <div class="card">
                            <img src="/Images/slider+news_be.jpg" alt="">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="card-title text-center">News</div>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    News provides current and relevant information about events, developments, and trends happening locally and globally. It serves as a critical source of knowledge, helping individuals stay informed, make informed decisions, and engage in discussions about the world around them. With the advent of digital media, news is now accessible through various platforms, including newspapers, television, and online sources.
                                </p>
                                <a href="" class="btn btn-success d-grid col-md-6 offset-3">Read More...</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mt-3">
                        <div class="card" style="height:100%;">
                            <img src="/Images/entertainment .jpg" alt="">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="card-title text-center">Entertainment</div>
                                <p class="card-text">Entertainment is a diverse and creative industry that offers enjoyment and diversion to people through various forms of media and live performances. It includes music, films, television shows, theater, sports, and more. Entertainment serves as a means of relaxation, escapism, and cultural enrichment, contributing significantly to people's overall well-being and quality of life.</p>
                                <a href="" class="btn btn-success d-grid col-md-6 offset-3">Read More...</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="container-fluid mt-3">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4 mt-3">
                        <div class="card">
                            <img src="/Images/business.jpg" alt="">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="card-title text-center">Business</div>
                                <p class="card-text">Business is the economic engine of society, encompassing a wide spectrum of activities, from small startups to multinational corporations. It involves the production, distribution, and exchange of goods and services, with the goal of generating profit. Business plays a vital role in driving economic growth, creating employment opportunities, and shaping global markets.</p>
                                <a href="" class="btn btn-success d-grid col-md-6 offset-3">Read More...</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="card mt-3" style="height:96%;">
                            <img src="/Images/Fitness.jpg" alt="">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="card-title text-center">Fitness</div>
                                <p class="card-text">Fitness is a state of physical and mental well-being achieved through regular exercise, a balanced diet, and a healthy lifestyle. It promotes strength, endurance, flexibility, and overall vitality. Regular fitness activities improve both physical health and mental clarity, enhancing the quality of life.</p>
                                <a href="" class="btn btn-success d-grid col-md-6 offset-3">Read More...</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="card mt-3" style="height:96%;">
                            <img src="/Images/How-is-the-weather.jpg" alt="">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="card-title text-center">Weather</div>
                                <p class="card-text">Weather refers to the atmospheric conditions and phenomena in a specific location at a given time, encompassing factors such as temperature, humidity, precipitation, wind, and atmospheric pressure. It plays a crucial role in daily life, influencing activities, travel, and clothing choices. Weather patterns are closely monitored and predicted by meteorologists to ensure safety and preparedness for various conditions.</p>
                                <a href="" class="btn btn-success d-grid col-md-6 offset-3">Read More...</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
